{"tid":928581,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【水行俠】Jason Momoa試鏡「揸流灘」　因禍得福改演水行俠","createTime":"2018-12-05T02:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T15:04:22.000Z","uid":212399,"like":26,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"9363cab40f3cea8ea80440238cf2232a08dd1086","tid":928581,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T02:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2164021/org/03fe04437857e8de9974fc34954deb65.jpg/EKYk2DPEweLMg9DjfgZRbpOXCLkGnSJqUUFRF1FBURc?v=w1120r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2164021%2Forg%2F03fe04437857e8de9974fc34954deb65.jpg%2FEKYk2DPEweLMg9DjfgZRbpOXCLkGnSJqUUFRF1FBURc%3Fv%3Dw1120r16_9&h=85f65d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《水行俠》（Aquaman）上映在即，身為水行俠的Jason Momoa忙於為電影宣傳。近日他接受外國傳媒訪問時談到原本《蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光》（Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice）導演邀請他飾演蝙蝠俠一角。然而他覺得是一個「傻子陷阱」（Booby Trap），故他一直不想以傳統方式演出蝙蝠俠。最終他失落此角色。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2164295/org/0e0b0c7488b9430dfc5697d1644b62c2.jpg/2NvMyhAeieAoNYACxmypRbk9-NS0plTKjj8AZ44_AGc?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2164295%2Forg%2F0e0b0c7488b9430dfc5697d1644b62c2.jpg%2F2NvMyhAeieAoNYACxmypRbk9-NS0plTKjj8AZ44_AGc%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=7d6e8d49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有指導演Zack Snyder希望Jason Momoa成為蝙蝠俠。<br />\n事源是他接受外國傳媒《Fox Chicago》訪問，並談及當時獲《蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光》導演薩克薛達（Zack Snyder）邀請他為蝙蝠俠一角試鏡。他續指出，當時的試鏡是沿用《蝙蝠俠&mdash;黑夜之神》（The Dark Knight）場景：「這是一次重大的試鏡，很多人都希望能得到這機會。」，所以Jason Momoa改變演出方法：「我只是覺得這是一個傻子陷阱，我不想以傳統方式演蝙蝠俠。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2164294/org/0a073e1d5c5d98fe472d9f4b363061f4.jpg/uE6xJ0pzkcEJdunMpBz4PH0KArpZpWESMpRKsjKUSrI?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2164294%2Forg%2F0a073e1d5c5d98fe472d9f4b363061f4.jpg%2FuE6xJ0pzkcEJdunMpBz4PH0KArpZpWESMpRKsjKUSrI%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=000bca85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJason Momoa在《蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光》客串登場<br />\n雖然他最終都有出席試鏡，但他全程「揸流灘」：「我假裝蝙蝠俠被追殺至一條小巷，然後揣摩他的心態，他變得潦倒，即使是面對好人，他也不會害怕傷害他們。」，Jason Momoa指他把蝙蝠俠成為一個有瑕疵的人，如今，他承認自己演錯了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2164298/org/0bac58f5d001442cfc60b0f7f6291122.png/ZyshoYGpBqVF9Me_tBkrKTC93_dKChC_vvCne77wp3s?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2164298%2Forg%2F0bac58f5d001442cfc60b0f7f6291122.png%2FZyshoYGpBqVF9Me_tBkrKTC93_dKChC_vvCne77wp3s%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=a9cc7c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJason Momoa最終因禍得福，成為水行俠。<br />\n最終由賓艾佛力（Ben Affleck）擔任蝙蝠俠，然而賓艾佛力的蝙蝠俠一直為人詬病，看來最初他的選擇也非常正確。雖然不能成為蝙蝠俠，但薩克薛達同樣欣賞Jason Momoa當時的演出，並邀請他成為水行俠，成為亞特蘭提斯的國王。Jason Momoa表示，大約兩至三個星期後，導演薩克薛達就打電話給他，並叫他在出演《正義聯盟》前，先以水行俠一角在《蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光》中率先客串登場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2164313/org/e2d722189f65de8683617c4caf26f6cb.jpg/wdan7Q0EC210vnkFYf557QXUcQQAIFK2PgWpoj4FqaI?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2164313%2Forg%2Fe2d722189f65de8683617c4caf26f6cb.jpg%2Fwdan7Q0EC210vnkFYf557QXUcQQAIFK2PgWpoj4FqaI%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=83964aeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《正義聯盟》亦未能成功拒挽救DC電影的劣勢。<br />\n可是，據了解，當時他也想把水行俠一角推倒。他表示得知要成為水行俠時非常擔心，因為他不懂游泳。雖然他是夏威夷州血統的原住民，並在愛荷華大學攻讀海洋生物學，也是衝浪好手Brian Keaulana及Rusty Keaulana的侄子。不過因導演薩克薛達的賞識，他今次再沒有婉拒。如今，水行俠要準備出巡了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2164346/org/153f5c5035913bec89814769d3e4e6c0.jpg/O_QEiABPPJqpqPHf4VBIEYMcX_-oPHVwZ1rH7Gdax-w?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2164346%2Forg%2F153f5c5035913bec89814769d3e4e6c0.jpg%2FO_QEiABPPJqpqPHf4VBIEYMcX_-oPHVwZ1rH7Gdax-w%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=2498111b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《水行俠》首輪影評獲激讚，相信有望打救DC電影。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/電影/266394/水行俠-jason-momoa試鏡-揸流灘-因禍得福改演水行俠\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%2F266394%2F%E6%B0%B4%E8%A1%8C%E4%BF%A0-jason-momoa%E8%A9%A6%E9%8F%A1-%E6%8F%B8%E6%B5%81%E7%81%98-%E5%9B%A0%E7%A6%8D%E5%BE%97%E7%A6%8F%E6%94%B9%E6%BC%94%E6%B0%B4%E8%A1%8C%E4%BF%A0&d=7rHVLdsKJorL0mK4yt4KGP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1d86ea23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/電影/266394/水行俠-jason-momoa試鏡-揸流灘-因禍得福改演水行俠</a>"},{"pid":"d3accd40a226bd7a91249b99b21ff8d0ce6e6643","tid":928581,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T02:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fcb937a8031ef7e0aa853571292a93647460b3a","tid":928581,"uid":42152,"like":211,"dislike":0,"score":211,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T02:32:52.000Z","msg":"可是，據了解，當時他也想把水行俠一角推倒。他表示得知要成為水行俠時非常擔心，因為他不懂游泳。雖然他是夏威夷州血統的原住民，並在愛荷華大學攻讀海洋生物學，也是衝浪好手Brian Keaulana及Rusty Keaulana的侄子。<br />\n<br />\n好少鬼佬唔識游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6913e591963094333106637dbfd144c7323a7d40","tid":928581,"uid":186961,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T02:33:59.000Z","msg":"唔識游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089500a80486e5fdc7acb9668cbf6ffda8ad97e3","tid":928581,"uid":136421,"like":151,"dislike":0,"score":151,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T02:36:31.000Z","msg":"佢咁嘅款真係睇唔出唔識游泳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5788745ee51e3580d0731567fa89564d2302ca","tid":928581,"uid":135132,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T02:38:25.000Z","msg":"後生時明明拍過baywatch扮救生員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aad5727459eeb7ed7a99818f2ecf8cac2a69d08","tid":928581,"uid":136421,